WEBVTT

00:05.739 --> 00:06.974
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:07.007 --> 00:09.610
IF I WAS SHOT IN MY
JERK‐OFF ARM, I'D BE MAD, TOO.

00:09.643 --> 00:12.746
I CAN MAKE THE PAIN GO AWAY
ANYTIME WITH A PILL,

00:12.779 --> 00:14.014
BUT I DON'T WANT TO.

00:14.047 --> 00:15.916
[ HORN BLARING ]
HEY, FUCK YOU, MAN.

00:15.949 --> 00:16.917
[ LAUGHS ]

00:16.950 --> 00:19.386
[ GRUNTING ]

00:19.419 --> 00:20.821
THEY SMOKED HEROIN.

00:20.854 --> 00:21.889
HER FRIENDS SUCK.

00:21.922 --> 00:23.657
Silas:
SHE KIND OF SUCKS.

00:23.690 --> 00:26.193
I'M GONNA OUT‐NANCY NANCY.

00:26.226 --> 00:28.795
YOU TWO IDIOTS WANT TO
GET BACK AT MOM, RIGHT?

00:28.829 --> 00:30.597
ALL RIGHT, THEN.
LET'S DO THIS RIGHT.

00:30.631 --> 00:33.400
YOU KNOW WHAT? I COULD
USE A LITTLE MORE SNAKE
BITE, I THINK, FOR MY LIPS.

00:33.433 --> 00:36.370
NANCY, IT'S ME.
THE COPS ARE AFTER ME.

00:36.403 --> 00:39.740
I HAVE THIS BAG
FULL OF PLANTS.

00:39.773 --> 00:41.508
I need your help.

00:41.542 --> 00:42.609
BINGO!

00:42.643 --> 00:44.411
Audra: I KNEW IT WAS A BAD IDEA
HAVING YOU PICK ME UP.

00:44.444 --> 00:47.748
GAYLE HAS A THING FOR ME.
THEY'RE DANGEROUS, ANDY.

00:47.781 --> 00:48.949
FORNICATORS!

00:48.982 --> 00:50.417
I'M GONNA ASK AUDRA
TO MARRY ME.

00:50.450 --> 00:52.619
I WANT TO GIVE HER
MY MOM'S ENGAGEMENT RING,

00:52.653 --> 00:54.154
THE RING
THAT JUDAH GAVE YOU.

00:54.188 --> 00:55.189
SO, CAN I HAVE IT?

00:55.222 --> 00:57.891
PILAR ZUAZO.
I WANT HER DEAD.

00:57.925 --> 00:59.193
DEPENDS IF YOU
CAN HELP ME OUT.

00:59.226 --> 01:01.395
HELP GET MY CASE
TRANSFERRED TO MEXICO.

01:01.428 --> 01:03.297
ESTEBAN REYES?

01:06.834 --> 01:08.836
HE'S NOT HERE.
WHAT?

01:08.869 --> 01:10.804
HE WAS RELEASED
FOUR HOURS AGO.

01:10.838 --> 01:12.739
HE'S BACK ON THE TICKET.

01:12.773 --> 01:15.209
SHE PULLED HIM BACK IN.

01:27.855 --> 01:30.023
Candela: vSEÑORA?

01:38.866 --> 01:40.901
GOOD MORNING.

01:40.934 --> 01:43.504
I'LL STEP OUTSIDE
SO YOU CAN GET UNDRESSED.

01:43.537 --> 01:45.005
W‐WHAT IS THIS?

01:45.038 --> 01:46.807
A GIFT FOR YOU.

01:46.840 --> 01:48.609
OH, NO, THANK YOU.
I DON'T WANT IT.

01:48.642 --> 01:51.545
I CAN'T LEAVE THIS ROOM
UNTIL I'VE DONE MY JOB.

01:51.578 --> 01:52.613
PLEASE LEAVE.

01:52.646 --> 01:54.882
I CAN SEE YOU NEED ME.

01:54.915 --> 01:58.852
LET ME HELP YOU.

01:58.886 --> 02:02.089
DON'T MAKE ME SIT ON YOU.

02:03.824 --> 02:05.292
RELAX.

02:05.325 --> 02:06.593
RELAX.

02:06.627 --> 02:07.895
SORRY.

02:07.928 --> 02:09.496
DON'T BE SORRY.
JUST BE LIMP.

02:09.530 --> 02:11.899
DO YOU KNOW MY HUSBAND'S
RUNNING FOR GOVERNOR?

02:11.932 --> 02:14.501
YES, I HEARD.
CONGRATULATIONS.

02:14.535 --> 02:17.404
NOW RELAX AND BREATHE.

02:17.437 --> 02:18.872
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

02:18.906 --> 02:21.909
[ INHALES,
EXHALES DEEPLY ]

02:21.942 --> 02:23.010
HE'S A PUPPET.

02:23.043 --> 02:24.511
YOU BE MY PUPPET.

02:24.545 --> 02:27.147
LET ME PULL THE STRINGS.

02:28.582 --> 02:29.983
MEN ARE WEAK.

02:30.017 --> 02:31.685
SOME MEN ARE WEAK.

02:34.021 --> 02:35.756
WOMEN ARE STRONG...

02:35.789 --> 02:38.692
UNTIL THEY...FALL APART.

02:38.725 --> 02:40.227
YOU'RE NOT GOING
TO FALL APART.

02:40.260 --> 02:42.229
OH, NO?
WHAT MAKES YOU SO SURE?

02:42.262 --> 02:45.332
YOU'RE A WARRIOR...
LIKE THE BOSS.

02:45.365 --> 02:48.735
VERY SIMILAR, LOCKED UP
IN ALL THE SAME PLACES.

02:48.769 --> 02:49.736
[ SIGHS ]

02:49.770 --> 02:52.506
ARMORED
AND READY FOR BATTLE.

02:52.539 --> 02:53.407
YEAH.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.642
AT LEAST WE STILL HAVE THAT
IN COMMON.

02:55.676 --> 02:59.146
YOU'D BE SURPRISED HOW MUCH
YOU HAVE IN COMMON WITH PILAR.

03:02.382 --> 03:04.051
PILAR?

03:04.084 --> 03:06.053
YES.
SHE SENT ME TO YOU.

03:06.086 --> 03:09.756
SHE WANTED YOU FEELING RELAXED
AND WELL.

03:09.790 --> 03:11.725
DID WE DO THE JOB?

03:43.257 --> 03:45.926
THERE YOU ARE,
YOU FERAL BITCH.

03:45.959 --> 03:47.060
STOP RIGHT THERE.

03:47.094 --> 03:49.263
I'M DIGGIN' THE HAIR.

03:49.296 --> 03:52.065
YOU GOT THIS WHOLE
CRAZY GYPSY THING GOING ON.

03:52.099 --> 03:53.934
WANT TO LICK
MY CRYSTAL BALLS?

03:53.967 --> 03:55.903
I HAVE A PROPOSITION
FOR YOU.

03:55.936 --> 03:57.804
DOES IT INVOLVE
LICKING MY CRYSTAL BALLS?

03:57.838 --> 04:00.941
I HAVE SOME PRODUCT
I'M TRYING TO UNLOAD,

04:00.974 --> 04:03.210
AND I'LL LET IT GO CHEAP.

04:03.243 --> 04:05.812
FIRE SALE.
I'M OUT OF HERE.

04:05.846 --> 04:07.848
I‐I'M GETTING OUT
OF THIS BUSINESS.

04:07.881 --> 04:09.316
SINCE WHEN ARE YOU
IN THE BUSINESS?

04:10.350 --> 04:12.519
ANYWAY, I'M BROKE.
HOW BROKE?

04:12.553 --> 04:13.720
I GOT $37.

04:13.754 --> 04:15.522
UGH! CRAP.

04:15.556 --> 04:16.857
[ SIGHS ]

04:16.890 --> 04:18.692
HOW ABOUT THIS?

04:18.725 --> 04:23.197
YOU TAKE MY STUFF ON CREDIT,
YOU REOPEN THAT LITTLE SHOP,

04:23.230 --> 04:25.966
AND THEN PAY ME BACK
IN A TIMELY FASHION.

04:25.999 --> 04:27.868
AND IF YOU SCREW ME
ON THE DEAL,

04:27.901 --> 04:29.937
I'LL HAVE YOUR LEGS BROKEN
BY A MEXICAN GOON.

04:29.970 --> 04:31.805
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

04:31.839 --> 04:33.540
DEAL?

04:33.574 --> 04:34.708
[ SMACKS LIPS ]

04:34.741 --> 04:36.443
LET ME SEE WHAT YOU GOT.

04:43.350 --> 04:45.152
THAT'S NOT MY POT.
WHERE'D YOU GET <i>THIS?</i>

04:45.185 --> 04:46.820
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

04:46.854 --> 04:48.922
NOTHING.

04:48.956 --> 04:51.959
OH, MY GOD!
[ GASPS ]

04:51.992 --> 04:53.427
YOU KNOW!

04:53.460 --> 04:54.294
KNOW WHAT?

04:54.328 --> 04:58.031
OH, CHRIST. OF COURSE.
FUCKING DEAN.

04:58.065 --> 05:01.768
YOU'RE
THE WORST ACTOR EVER!

05:01.802 --> 05:03.070
WHERE'S MY POT,
YOU STINKY GASH?

05:03.103 --> 05:04.671
MY POT‐STORE POT!

05:04.705 --> 05:06.940
I SOLD YOUR
POT‐STORE POT.
THEN WHERE'S
MY FUCKING MONEY?

05:06.974 --> 05:09.076
I RENTED A CONDO
AND BOUGHT THIS POT.

05:09.109 --> 05:10.744
THEN THIS IS MY POT,
AND YOU OWE ME.

05:10.777 --> 05:12.379
NO, I AM NOT
LETTING YOU HAVE THAT.

05:12.412 --> 05:13.947
I'VE WORKED TOO HARD
FOR IT.

05:13.981 --> 05:16.083
A MINUTE AGO, YOU WERE BEGGING
ME TO TAKE THIS.

05:16.116 --> 05:17.351
THAT'S 'CAUSE THE HEAT IS ON.

05:17.384 --> 05:19.286
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
YOU CAN JUST TAKE IT!

05:19.319 --> 05:20.621
THAT'S RIGHT
THE HEAT IS ON.

05:20.654 --> 05:22.656
I'M GONNA CALL THAT BLACK COP
AND HAVE YOU ARRESTED.

05:22.689 --> 05:23.790
W‐WAIT...

05:23.824 --> 05:26.894
HOW DID YOU KNOW
HE WAS BLACK?

05:26.927 --> 05:28.862
WHAT?

05:28.896 --> 05:31.732
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

05:32.499 --> 05:34.168
OOH!

05:37.337 --> 05:39.673
[ SIGHS ]

05:45.979 --> 05:48.348
I THOUGHT
YOU WERE BREAST‐FEEDING.

05:48.382 --> 05:52.286
I HAD A LITTLE TOO MUCH TO DRINK
LAST NIGHT.

05:52.319 --> 05:53.554
OH.

05:53.587 --> 05:54.855
OH.

05:54.888 --> 05:56.590
I KNOW.

05:56.623 --> 05:59.393
HERE I GO, FAILING
YET ANOTHER ONE OF MY CHILDREN.

05:59.426 --> 06:01.028
I DIDN'T SAY THAT.

06:01.061 --> 06:02.229
NO, YOU DIDN'T.

06:02.262 --> 06:04.932
YOU DON'T SAY MUCH OF ANYTHING
TO ME ANYMORE.

06:04.965 --> 06:06.834
WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO SAY?

06:06.867 --> 06:09.236
I DON'T KNOW.

06:11.939 --> 06:14.641
SO...

06:14.675 --> 06:15.943
THERE WE ARE.

06:15.976 --> 06:17.945
YOU SHOULD GO
FEED THE BABY.

06:17.978 --> 06:20.514
Silas: HEY, GUYS.

06:24.151 --> 06:26.320
I'VE GOT TO GO
FEED THE BABY.

06:26.353 --> 06:28.555
THEN YOU
SHOULD DO THAT.

06:28.589 --> 06:30.991
I FED BOTH OF YOU.

06:31.024 --> 06:34.728
BREAST‐FED BOTH OF YOU.

06:34.761 --> 06:36.129
I DID.

06:38.432 --> 06:40.901
WELL, THANKS.

06:40.934 --> 06:43.704
YOU'RE WELCOME.

06:46.540 --> 06:47.875
WEIRDNESS.

06:47.908 --> 06:50.377
SHE'S MOM.

06:50.410 --> 06:53.113
SHE'S MOM.

06:54.114 --> 06:56.750
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:56.783 --> 06:58.285
WHO IS IT?

06:58.318 --> 06:59.620
ADELITA.

06:59.653 --> 07:01.855
SHE PROBABLY SNUCK OUT
TO SEE THOSE FUCKING IDIOTS

07:01.889 --> 07:02.856
AND CAN'T GET IN.

07:02.890 --> 07:04.892
HELLO?

07:04.925 --> 07:06.393
HEY.

07:06.426 --> 07:08.228
WHERE ARE YOU?

07:08.262 --> 07:09.796
I'LL...

07:09.830 --> 07:12.032
BE THERE IN A SEC.

07:12.065 --> 07:13.200
WHERE IS SHE?

07:13.233 --> 07:15.169
SHE'S HERE...
IN HER ROOM.

07:15.202 --> 07:17.604
SHE WANTS ME
TO COME UP THERE.

07:17.638 --> 07:19.072
WEAR A CONDOM.

07:19.106 --> 07:20.340
YOU LEARNED THAT LESSON,
HUH?

07:20.374 --> 07:21.141
OR DON'T.

07:21.175 --> 07:22.376
SEE WHAT'LL HAPPEN.

07:22.409 --> 07:24.778
MAYBE SHE SLEPT WITH SOMEONE
WHO SLEPT WITH SOMEONE

07:24.811 --> 07:26.180
WHO SLEPT
WITH SOMEONE FAMOUS.

07:26.213 --> 07:28.182
YOU COULD GET
GWYNETH PALTROW'S HERPES

07:28.215 --> 07:30.684
OR LADY GAGA'S
GENITAL WARTS.

07:30.717 --> 07:33.754
I HEAR EVERYONE IS DYING
FOR JOHN MAYER'S SYPHILIS.

07:33.787 --> 07:35.756
WHERE DO YOU GET
YOUR INTEL?

07:35.789 --> 07:38.091
I MAKE IT UP.

07:39.760 --> 07:41.395
[ SCOFFS ]

07:41.428 --> 07:42.863
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

07:42.896 --> 07:43.864
HEY!

07:43.897 --> 07:45.098
HEY, THERE.

07:45.132 --> 07:47.234
UM...
[ SIGHS ]

07:47.267 --> 07:50.571
DO YOU SEE ‐‐ SEE MY LAPTOP
OVER THERE ON MY DESK?

07:50.604 --> 07:52.506
YEAH.

07:52.539 --> 07:55.909
YEAH, UH, COULD YOU LOOK ‐‐
LOOK UP ‐‐

07:55.943 --> 07:58.545
COULD YOU
JUST BRING IT TO ME?

07:58.579 --> 08:04.117
UH, JUST, UH, JUST PUT IT
ON THE BED BY THIS HAND

08:04.151 --> 08:07.855
AND...OPEN IT FOR ME
AND GO.

08:07.888 --> 08:10.791
YOU CALLED ME UP HERE
TO GET YOUR LAPTOP,

08:10.824 --> 08:13.760
WHICH IS 4 FEET AWAY
FROM YOUR BED?

08:13.794 --> 08:15.596
GO FUCK YOURSELF,
PRINCESS.

08:15.629 --> 08:16.763
NO.

08:16.797 --> 08:18.799
SILAS, WAIT.

08:18.832 --> 08:20.000
[ SIGHS ]

08:20.033 --> 08:23.537
HEY...
HALF MY BODY'S GONE NUMB.

08:23.570 --> 08:27.975
I‐I JUST WANT TO GO ONLINE
AND TRY TO FIND OUT WHY.

08:28.008 --> 08:31.311
YOU WANT TO GOOGLE
WHY HALF YOUR BODY IS NUMB?

08:31.345 --> 08:32.145
YES.

08:32.179 --> 08:33.747
YOU COULD BE
HAVING A STROKE.

08:33.780 --> 08:35.015
I'M NOT HAVING A STROKE.

08:35.048 --> 08:37.451
OKAY? THIS ‐‐
THIS HAS HAPPENED BEFORE.

08:37.484 --> 08:40.754
WELL...IT WAS ‐‐
IT WAS JUST MY HAND, OKAY?

08:40.787 --> 08:44.958
'CAUSE I‐I HIT A NERVE ONE TIME
I SLAMMED INTO MY WRIST.

08:44.992 --> 08:46.827
IT WAS ‐‐ IT WAS DUMB.

08:46.860 --> 08:47.928
SLAMMED?

08:47.961 --> 08:49.763
INJECTED.

08:50.797 --> 08:51.965
HEROIN.

08:51.999 --> 08:54.635
HOLY SHIT!

08:54.668 --> 08:55.769
YOU'RE A JUNKIE.

08:55.802 --> 08:57.838
I AM A RECREATIONAL USER,
OKAY?

08:57.871 --> 08:58.972
FUCK YOU!

08:59.006 --> 09:01.508
IS THIS FROM THE STUFF
YOU WERE SMOKING?

09:01.542 --> 09:02.976
NO.

09:03.010 --> 09:06.847
IT...I THINK IT WAS...
FROM THE STUFF I‐I TOOK LATER.

09:06.880 --> 09:08.048
OH. PERFECT.

09:08.081 --> 09:09.883
I'M CALLING YOUR DAD.

09:09.917 --> 09:12.653
DON'T YOU FUCKING DARE!
OKAY?

09:12.686 --> 09:13.887
I THOUGHT YOU WERE COOL.

09:13.921 --> 09:16.356
YOU NEVER THOUGHT
I WAS COOL.

09:16.390 --> 09:17.691
THAT'S TRUE.

09:17.724 --> 09:19.293
JUST ‐‐
JUST GET OUT OF HERE.

09:19.326 --> 09:21.495
I DON'T KNOW
WHY I CALLED YOU ANYWAY.

09:21.528 --> 09:23.897
JUST ‐‐ I'LL BE FINE.

09:23.931 --> 09:25.732
SURE.

09:25.766 --> 09:26.900
GOOD LUCK TO YOU.

09:26.934 --> 09:28.902
WAIT! SILAS.

09:28.936 --> 09:31.305
SILAS...

09:31.338 --> 09:36.276
COULD YOU MAYBE SHOOT ME UP
JUST ONCE BEFORE YOU GO?

09:36.310 --> 09:39.012
YOU'VE GOT
TO BE KIDDING ME.

09:40.581 --> 09:41.715
[ RETCHES ]

09:41.748 --> 09:43.150
[ COUGHING, GAGGING ]

09:43.183 --> 09:45.085
Andy: OKAY, READY?

09:46.887 --> 09:47.855
I'M NOT SURE.

09:47.888 --> 09:49.890
OKAY, GET READY THEN.
OKAY.

09:49.923 --> 09:51.091
THIS IS SEXY.
SEXY?

09:51.124 --> 09:53.660
YEAH, SEXY.
OKAY.

09:55.295 --> 09:56.096
SEXY?

09:56.129 --> 09:57.965
UH‐HUH, SEXY.

09:57.998 --> 09:59.967
YOU'RE TURNED ON, HUH?

10:00.000 --> 10:01.735
IT'S A FLEX FUEL.

10:01.768 --> 10:03.303
I REGISTERED IT
UNDER A PSEUDONYM

10:03.337 --> 10:04.938
SO THE WHACKOS
CAN'T TRACE IT.

10:04.972 --> 10:06.507
I UNLISTED OUR PHONE NUMBER.

10:06.540 --> 10:07.407
YOU SOLD GENERAL LEE.

10:07.441 --> 10:09.276
YEAH, AND, UH,
AND THE SLOT MACHINE

10:09.309 --> 10:11.812
AND THE AIR HOCKEY
AND, UH, A FEW OTHER THINGS.

10:11.845 --> 10:12.946
NOT MS. PAC‐MAN.

10:12.980 --> 10:14.348
NO.
WHAT ARE YOU, CRAZY?

10:14.381 --> 10:16.950
I MEAN, I LOVE YOU, BUT I'VE
KNOWN MS. PAC‐MAN A LOT LONGER.

10:16.984 --> 10:18.585
SHE'LL ALWAYS
HAVE A PLACE IN MY HEART,

10:18.619 --> 10:21.188
SO IF YOU'RE THREATENED,
THEN WE NEED TO TALK IT OUT.

10:21.221 --> 10:22.723
I WANT TO SEE INSIDE.

10:22.756 --> 10:24.992
ALL RIGHT. WATCH THIS.

10:27.928 --> 10:29.963
OOH, THAT'S NICE.

10:29.997 --> 10:31.832
HMM?
YEAH!

10:31.865 --> 10:34.134
SEE, IT'S ALL ABOUT THE ‐‐
THE GLIDE.

10:34.168 --> 10:36.803
I'M THINKING "GREASED LIGHTNING"
OR "MELVIN."

10:36.837 --> 10:39.139
HAVEN'T SETTLED ON A NAME
FOR HIM YET.

10:39.173 --> 10:40.841
THIS IS LIKE A LIVING ROOM.

10:40.874 --> 10:43.544
YEAH.
COME SIT IN THE FRONT.

10:44.711 --> 10:46.346
[ GRUNTS ]

10:46.380 --> 10:47.981
OKAY.

10:48.015 --> 10:50.584
[ MUSIC PLAYS ]
NICE. COME ON.

10:50.617 --> 10:52.819
OH, MY GOD, THERE'S TWO
TV SCREENS. THAT'S BONKERS!

10:52.853 --> 10:55.222
DON'T MAKE ME
COME BACK THERE.

10:55.255 --> 10:56.657
COME ON.

10:56.690 --> 10:58.358
FINE. HERE I COME.

10:58.392 --> 11:00.727
[ GRUNTS ]

11:00.761 --> 11:01.728
AHH.

11:01.762 --> 11:03.764
OOH, THIS FEELS GOOD.

11:03.797 --> 11:05.599
OOH, A LITTLE
LUMBAR SUPPORT. GREAT.

11:05.632 --> 11:08.802
UM, WHAT IF WE GOT ONE
OF THOSE, UH, PINE‐TREE
AIR FRESHENERS?

11:08.836 --> 11:10.571
WHERE WOULD WE PUT THAT?

11:10.604 --> 11:12.806
OH, I HATE THOSE THINGS.
THEY MAKE ME SNEEZE.

11:12.840 --> 11:14.775
AND THEN WE'D LOSE
OUR NEW‐CAR SMELL.

11:14.808 --> 11:16.210
OOH, WOW, GPS.

11:16.243 --> 11:17.911
GOD DAMN IT,
LOOK AT THE REARVIEW MIRROR.

11:17.945 --> 11:19.112
WHAT? IS THERE SOMETHING
BEHIND US?

11:19.146 --> 11:21.048
NO, THERE'S NOTHING
BEHIND US.

11:21.081 --> 11:22.716
EVERYTHING'S
IN FRONT OF US.

11:22.749 --> 11:26.553
EVERYTHING IS IN FRONT OF US,
SO JUST ‐‐ OH, LOOK.

11:28.555 --> 11:30.591
YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULDN'T
LEAVE THAT THERE.

11:30.624 --> 11:33.126
IF THE LIGHT HITS THAT AND IT
GETS REFRACTED INTO YOUR EYES,

11:33.160 --> 11:36.897
IT COULD MOMENTARILY BLIND YOU,
AND YOU COULD CRASH.

11:36.930 --> 11:39.900
SO MAYBE
I SHOULD TAKE IT DOWN.

11:39.933 --> 11:41.869
YEAH.
JUST TO BE SAFE.

11:41.902 --> 11:42.870
YEAH.

11:42.903 --> 11:46.039
WANT TO MARRY ME
JUST TO BE SAFE?

11:47.574 --> 11:49.276
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

11:49.309 --> 11:50.277
FUCK!

11:50.310 --> 11:51.845
HELLO?

11:51.879 --> 11:53.180
Silas: Audra?
Oh, thank God.

11:53.213 --> 11:55.482
YEAH, SHE CAN'T TALK
RIGHT NOW, BUDDY,

11:55.516 --> 11:56.550
AND NEITHER CAN I.

11:56.583 --> 11:57.551
GOT TO GO, BAD TIMING.

11:57.584 --> 11:59.786
No, Andy, please,
I have to talk to Audra.

11:59.820 --> 12:00.787
It's an emergency.

12:00.821 --> 12:02.656
YOU'RE KILLING ME!

12:02.689 --> 12:04.691
OOH, DID SOMEONE ELSE
GET SHOT?

12:07.961 --> 12:11.164
Pilar:
DID YOU ENJOY YOUR MASSAGE?

12:11.198 --> 12:13.100
CANDELA IS MAGICAL.

12:13.133 --> 12:16.837
YES. MAGICAL.

12:16.870 --> 12:19.006
NOT AS MAGICAL AS ESTEBAN.

12:19.039 --> 12:23.644
HE DISAPPEARS,
HE REAPPEARS.

12:23.677 --> 12:27.014
ESTEBAN AND I CAN NEVER STAY
MAD AT EACH OTHER FOR TOO LONG.

12:27.047 --> 12:28.015
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:28.048 --> 12:31.518
WE'VE ALWAYS BEEN
A GREAT TEAM.

12:31.552 --> 12:35.923
SO...I'M GUESSING DEATH
AND/OR BLACKMAIL

12:35.956 --> 12:40.794
AND/OR, UH,
IMPRISONMENT IS THE...

12:40.827 --> 12:42.930
GLUE THAT HOLDS YOU
TOGETHER.

12:42.963 --> 12:45.699
WE HAVE COME
TO AN UNDERSTANDING.

12:45.732 --> 12:49.770
I'M...SO HAPPY
FOR YOU BOTH.

12:49.803 --> 12:51.839
I THOUGHT YOU
WERE BAD FOR HIM.

12:51.872 --> 12:54.474
THE POLLSTERS
HAVE TOLD ME OTHERWISE.

12:54.508 --> 12:57.878
YOU KNOW, I CAN ADMIT
WHEN I'VE MADE A MISTAKE.

12:57.911 --> 13:00.581
HE WILL WIN,
EVEN MARRIED TO YOU.

13:00.614 --> 13:05.085
BUT...IT WOULD STILL BE BEST
IF YOU STAYED IN THE BACKGROUND.

13:05.118 --> 13:06.820
OH, DON'T ‐‐
DON'T MIND ME.

13:06.854 --> 13:08.589
CAN YOU LEAVE MY HOUSE NOW?

13:08.622 --> 13:09.590
NANCY.

13:09.623 --> 13:11.391
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT'S OKAY.

13:11.425 --> 13:14.728
I SHOULD GO TO PREPARE
FOR THE PARTY TONIGHT.

13:14.761 --> 13:16.763
BIG PARTY
AT MY HOUSE, NANCY.

13:16.797 --> 13:19.199
FUNDRAISER
FOR THE CAMPAIGN.

13:19.233 --> 13:21.368
YOU SHOULD COME ‐‐
FOR 30 MINUTES.

13:21.401 --> 13:23.971
THEN YOU WILL GET A HEADACHE
AND LEAVE.

13:24.004 --> 13:28.275
I PROMISE TO DELIVER HIM
BACK BEFORE DAWN.

13:28.308 --> 13:32.045
ADIOS.

13:36.850 --> 13:39.686
SO...

13:39.720 --> 13:41.889
YOU HAD SOME DAY
YESTERDAY.

13:41.922 --> 13:43.891
YES.

13:43.924 --> 13:46.460
I WENT LOOKING FOR YOU.

13:46.493 --> 13:48.095
I KNOW.

13:48.128 --> 13:53.834
I FOUND YOU...ON TV.

13:53.867 --> 13:55.836
YOU LOOK GOOD ON TV.

13:55.869 --> 13:57.437
YOU KNOW...

13:57.471 --> 14:01.775
SHE HAS EVERYTHING...

14:01.808 --> 14:06.813
EVERY INDISCRETION...
DOCUMENTED...

14:06.847 --> 14:09.850
PHOTOGRAPHED.

14:09.883 --> 14:11.685
I COULD COOPERATE.

14:11.718 --> 14:14.788
I COULD GO TO PRISON
FOR LIFE.

14:14.821 --> 14:16.924
THOSE WERE MY OPTIONS.

14:16.957 --> 14:19.726
WHAT WOULD
YOU HAVE ME DO?

14:38.812 --> 14:44.117
IS THAT ‐‐ ARE YOU WEARING
MY DEODORANT?

14:45.686 --> 14:46.854
IT'S FOR MEN.

14:46.887 --> 14:48.722
I LIKE IT.

14:48.755 --> 14:52.693
I DON'T WANT TO HAVE MY NOSE
IN YOUR ARMPIT AND SMELL MYSELF.

14:52.726 --> 14:54.928
SO DON'T PUT YOUR NOSE
IN MY ARMPIT.

14:54.962 --> 14:57.865
NO.
DO YOU HEAR ME?

14:57.898 --> 15:00.834
I DON'T LIKE YOU
WEARING IT.

15:00.868 --> 15:03.837
I‐I‐I LIKE THE WAY
IT SMELLS.

15:03.871 --> 15:05.105
YOU SMELL LIKE A MAN.

15:05.138 --> 15:07.774
YOU WILL NOT WEAR IT AGAIN.

15:07.808 --> 15:09.843
IS THAT CLEAR?

15:09.877 --> 15:12.546
YEAH.

15:12.579 --> 15:13.881
I GOT IT.

15:13.914 --> 15:15.983
YOU'RE THE MAN.

15:18.819 --> 15:21.355
[ Cellphone ringing ]

15:22.322 --> 15:24.758
YOU KNOW,
I WAS JUST THINKING ABOUT YOU.

15:24.791 --> 15:26.593
I saw a dogfight
last night.

15:26.627 --> 15:30.797
TWO PIT‐BULL BITCHES RIPPED
THE SHIT OUT OF EACH OTHER.

15:30.831 --> 15:33.700
ONE OF THEM
HAD A REALLY NICE ASS.

15:33.734 --> 15:35.435
WHERE ARE YOU?

15:35.469 --> 15:36.537
Mexico.

15:36.570 --> 15:37.738
THANKS, BLANCA.

15:37.771 --> 15:40.707
YOU KNOW,
IT'S NICE TO BE FREE.

15:40.741 --> 15:41.842
That was fast.

15:41.875 --> 15:44.211
YEAH.
YOU DID GOOD BY ME.

15:44.244 --> 15:47.481
I WANT IT DONE TODAY,
GUILLERMO ‐‐ TODAY.

15:47.514 --> 15:50.851
I HELD UP MY END.
JUST ‐‐ JUST...DO IT.

15:50.884 --> 15:52.920
SURE. IT'S NO PROBLEM.

15:52.953 --> 15:54.988
I'M YOUR BOY, RIGHT?

15:59.293 --> 16:02.162
[ SIGHS ]

16:04.031 --> 16:06.233
[ MUNCHING ]

16:08.235 --> 16:11.004
SO, YOU'RE BENEFITING
FROM MY EXPERIENCE.

16:11.038 --> 16:14.708
WHEN QUINN TIED ME UP,
I CHAFED.

16:14.741 --> 16:16.777
YOU SHOULD BE
PRETTY COMFORTABLE.

16:16.810 --> 16:19.913
SO, WHAT HAPPENS NOW?

16:19.947 --> 16:21.181
WELL, I GO BACK

16:21.215 --> 16:23.917
TO MY FABULOUSLY SUCCESSFUL
CAREER AS A DRUG DEALER

16:23.951 --> 16:28.088
BECAUSE THERE ARE NO BLACK COPS
LOOKING FOR ME.

16:28.121 --> 16:29.456
WHAT HAPPENS TO <i>ME?</i>

16:29.489 --> 16:30.324
MM.

16:30.357 --> 16:32.826
I HAVEN'T
THOUGHT THAT THROUGH YET.

16:32.860 --> 16:34.228
I COULD SELL YOUR ORGANS.

16:34.261 --> 16:35.662
WELL, YOU'VE HAD
THE BEST ONE.

16:35.696 --> 16:37.431
I DON'T DO DICK ANYMORE.

16:37.464 --> 16:38.932
DO TELL.

16:38.966 --> 16:40.601
[ Singsong voice ]
I MET A LADY.

16:40.634 --> 16:41.835
NICE.

16:41.869 --> 16:44.204
SHE IS NICE,
NICE TO ME.

16:44.238 --> 16:47.541
SHE UNDERSTANDS
HOW A WOMAN WORKS.

16:47.574 --> 16:50.811
WHEN WE KISS, IT'S SOFT,

16:50.844 --> 16:53.280
AND OUR BREASTS
PRESS AGAINST EACH OTHER

16:53.313 --> 16:55.482
AND ‐‐
OH, WHO AM I KIDDING?

16:55.516 --> 16:56.783
I NEED DICK.

16:56.817 --> 16:58.385
WHO IS SHE?

16:58.418 --> 16:59.786
SHE SELLS COSMETICS.

16:59.820 --> 17:01.588
YOU FUCKED RAYLENE?

17:01.622 --> 17:03.090
YOU KNOW HER?

17:03.123 --> 17:04.858
I TRIED TO KNOW HER,
BUT SHE LIKES GIRL PARTS.

17:04.892 --> 17:06.527
AND SUCCESS.

17:06.560 --> 17:09.129
YEAH, WELL, YOU PRETTY MUCH
STOLE ANY CHANCE I HAD AT <i>THAT.</i>

17:09.162 --> 17:10.497
WELL, SURVIVAL
OF THE FITTEST.

17:10.531 --> 17:12.499
YOU WERE STUPID.
AND YOU WERE GREEDY.

17:12.533 --> 17:14.535
OH, RIGHT. LIKE YOU WOULDN'T
HAVE DONE THE SAME THING.

17:14.568 --> 17:16.670
THAT'S NOT THE POINT.
OH, WELL, THEN WHAT IS?

17:16.703 --> 17:18.872
WE WERE BOTH GREEDY AND STUPID,
AND LOOK WHERE IT GOT US ‐‐

17:18.906 --> 17:20.340
SITTING HERE
IN SOME STORAGE LOCKER.

17:20.374 --> 17:21.975
YOU WITH THE STENCH OF PUSSY
ON YOUR LIPS

17:22.009 --> 17:24.144
AND ME WITH
A DRAWER‐DENTED DICK.

17:24.178 --> 17:27.681
WELL, SPEAK FOR YOURSELF,
'CAUSE I AM JUST FINE.

17:27.714 --> 17:29.816
TILL THE NEXT TIME YOU THINK
A COP'S WATCHING YOU.

17:29.850 --> 17:32.252
WOW, YOU FOLDED SO QUICK.

17:32.286 --> 17:34.688
MAYBE YOU'RE NOT
CUT OUT FOR THIS.

17:34.721 --> 17:37.024
NO! I WANT TO BE
A DRUG DEALER.

17:37.057 --> 17:38.158
[ SCOFFS ]

17:38.192 --> 17:40.928
IF NANCY CAN DO IT,
SO CAN I.

17:40.961 --> 17:42.462
HOW DID SHE DO IT?

17:42.496 --> 17:43.630
SHE HAD A TEAM.

17:43.664 --> 17:45.966
I NEED A TEAM.

17:45.999 --> 17:49.169
PEOPLE I CAN TRUST.

17:49.203 --> 17:51.171
I DON'T TRUST ANYBODY.

17:51.205 --> 17:53.073
THAT'S GONNA MAKE IT HARD
TO PUT TOGETHER A TEAM.

17:53.106 --> 17:55.642
NANCY HAD A TEAM.
I WANT A TEAM.

17:55.676 --> 17:57.678
DO YOU WANT TO
TEAM UP WITH ME?

17:57.711 --> 17:58.979
FUCK YOU.

17:59.012 --> 18:00.781
SO, WHO ARE YOU GONNA
TEAM UP WITH THEN?

18:00.814 --> 18:03.517
[ SIGHS ]

18:03.550 --> 18:05.252
FINE.

18:05.285 --> 18:06.587
BUT YOU TEAM UP WITH ME.

18:06.620 --> 18:08.789
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE
WHO TEAMS UP WITH WHO?

18:08.822 --> 18:09.990
IT MAKES
ALL THE DIFFERENCE.

18:10.023 --> 18:10.657
BOTTOM...TOP.

18:10.691 --> 18:12.226
YOU'RE TIED UP.

18:17.831 --> 18:20.400
[ SIGHS ]

18:21.468 --> 18:22.803
ANDY.

18:22.836 --> 18:23.804
OH, HI, NANCE.

18:23.837 --> 18:25.906
HI, NANCY.
NICE TO SEE YOU.

18:25.939 --> 18:27.708
TELL ME SOMEONE ELSE
HASN'T GOTTEN SHOT.

18:27.741 --> 18:29.810
NO, NO. IT'S ‐‐ I'M HERE TO SEE
MY NEPHEW AND SAY HI.

18:29.843 --> 18:31.812
THANK GOD.
SHE'S IN HE‐‐

18:31.845 --> 18:34.047
YOU SAID YOU WOULDN'T
SAY ANYTHING.

18:34.081 --> 18:36.316
SHE'S ROAMING THE HALLS.
I DON'T KNOW.

18:36.350 --> 18:38.318
WHAT THE FUCK
IS GOING ON?

18:38.352 --> 18:40.921
I THINK ADELITA O. D.'d
OR SOMETHING.

18:40.954 --> 18:44.057
O.D.'d ON WHAT?

18:45.359 --> 18:46.593
HEROIN.

18:46.627 --> 18:48.695
SHE'S A JUNKIE.

18:51.732 --> 18:55.068
HEY, SILAS,
UH, COME IN WITH ME.

18:55.102 --> 18:57.171
UM, I'LL FIND YOU WHEN I KNOW
A LITTLE BIT MORE.

18:57.204 --> 18:58.572
WE DON'T
WANT TO OVERWHELM HER.

18:58.605 --> 18:59.606
RIGHT.

18:59.640 --> 19:01.742
OKAY, SWEETIE, HEALER OF
THE SICK, SAVER OF LIVES.

19:01.775 --> 19:02.776
I LOVE YOU.

19:02.809 --> 19:03.877
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

19:03.911 --> 19:06.113
WOW.

19:06.146 --> 19:07.781
SO, YOU DID IT, HUH?

19:07.814 --> 19:09.816
I DID.
SHE'S A DOCTOR.

19:09.850 --> 19:11.919
I'M MARRYING A DOCTOR.

19:11.952 --> 19:14.788
AND SHE ACTUALLY
SAID YES?

19:14.821 --> 19:16.924
SHE WILL.
SHE'S HOOKED.

19:16.957 --> 19:18.759
UH, DING DONG?

19:18.792 --> 19:20.460
OH, YEAH.

19:22.462 --> 19:24.064
ADELITA'S A JUNKIE.

19:24.097 --> 19:27.267
UM, I THINK WITH THE ACCENT,
IT'S "YUNKIE."

19:29.803 --> 19:31.572
JESUS.

19:31.605 --> 19:34.241
FANCY BOARDING SCHOOLS,
THREE LANGUAGES,

19:34.274 --> 19:38.478
BUT A NEGLECTED CHILD
IS A NEGLECTED CHILD.

19:38.512 --> 19:39.947
YOU'RE GLOATING.

19:39.980 --> 19:41.915
WHAT?

19:41.949 --> 19:43.383
YOU'RE GLOATING.

19:43.417 --> 19:45.752
YOU'RE A LITTLE GLAD ESTEBAN'S
DAUGHTER'S A DRUG ADDICT.

19:45.786 --> 19:47.254
MORE THAN
A LITTLE GLAD.

19:47.287 --> 19:48.856
I AM NOT.
IT'S HORRIBLE.

19:48.889 --> 19:50.591
ESTEBAN'S
GONNA BE HEARTBROKEN.

19:50.624 --> 19:52.159
GLOATING.

19:52.192 --> 19:54.394
A‐A LITTLE.
NO, I'M NOT.

19:55.863 --> 19:57.865
HE DID
PUT DOWN MY CHILDREN,

19:57.898 --> 19:59.833
TOLD ME I SHOULD HAVE
SENT THEM AWAY.

19:59.867 --> 20:01.802
WOW.

20:01.835 --> 20:03.437
BLOOM IS OFF THE ROSE,
HUH?

20:03.470 --> 20:07.474
LITTLE SORRY THAT YOU PLEDGED
ETERNAL LOVE AND DEVOTION?

20:07.508 --> 20:08.742
I CAN'T RELY ON MEN.

20:08.775 --> 20:09.977
DOESN'T MEAN
I DON'T LOVE THEM.

20:10.010 --> 20:11.111
IT DOESN'T MEAN
I WALK OUT.

20:11.144 --> 20:14.781
IT JUST MEANS
I ADJUSTED MY EXPECTATIONS.

20:14.815 --> 20:17.784
MEN...ARE WEAK.

20:17.818 --> 20:20.854
I'M NOT.
I'M FUCKING STEEL.

20:20.888 --> 20:22.623
YES, YOU ARE.

20:22.656 --> 20:25.792
AND YOU'RE
GETTING MARRIED.

20:25.826 --> 20:27.628
YEP.

20:27.661 --> 20:30.197
WE'RE LIKE
AN O. HENRY STORY.

20:30.230 --> 20:31.832
NO.

20:31.865 --> 20:35.435
WE'RE OUR OWN
FUCKED‐UP LITTLE STORY.

20:40.007 --> 20:41.508
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:41.542 --> 20:42.976
WHY IS HE ALWAYS HERE?

20:43.010 --> 20:44.311
AFTERNOON.

20:44.344 --> 20:45.812
I LIKE HIM.

20:45.846 --> 20:48.849
HEY, CONGRATS
ON YOUR NEW RUN.

20:48.882 --> 20:50.651
YEAH, WELL, THANK YOU.

20:50.684 --> 20:52.452
SIT DOWN, JOIN US.

20:52.486 --> 20:54.788
ANDY JUST PROPOSED TO AUDRA
THIS MORNING.

20:54.821 --> 20:56.924
AH.
CONGRATULATIONS.

20:56.957 --> 21:00.928
MARRIAGE IS A COMPLICATED
AND DELICATE DANCE.

21:00.961 --> 21:02.462
Yeah. It is.

21:02.496 --> 21:03.830
SELL IT.

21:03.864 --> 21:05.199
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:05.232 --> 21:08.936
SO, WHY ‐‐ WHY ARE YOU HERE
AND NOT WITH YOUR FIANCéE?

21:08.969 --> 21:10.337
OH, SHE'S HERE, TOO.

21:10.370 --> 21:12.606
[ SCOFFS ]
WHO ELSE GOT SHOT?

21:12.639 --> 21:15.843
NOBODY GOT SHOT.
ADELITA WASN'T FEELING WELL.

21:15.876 --> 21:18.111
WHY DIDN'T
YOU TELL ME THAT?

21:18.145 --> 21:19.546
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

21:19.580 --> 21:20.914
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
I SHOULD GO SEE HER.

21:20.948 --> 21:22.015
NO, AUDRA'S
UP THERE WITH HER.

21:22.049 --> 21:24.518
YOU CAN GO AND SEE HER
IN A LITTLE WHILE.

21:24.551 --> 21:27.688
WHAT IS THE MATTER
WITH MY DAUGHTER?

21:30.891 --> 21:34.862
SHE IS PREGNANT,
ISN'T SHE?

21:34.895 --> 21:37.397
STUPID, STUPID GIRL.

21:37.431 --> 21:38.832
OH, COME ON NOW.

21:38.866 --> 21:40.200
I HEAR SHE SPEAKS
THREE LANGUAGES.

21:40.234 --> 21:42.836
SHE'S NOT PREGNANT,
ESTEBAN.

21:42.870 --> 21:47.007
S‐SHE HAS...
A HEROIN PROBLEM.

21:50.010 --> 21:52.713
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
ADELITA?

21:52.746 --> 21:54.381
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

21:56.850 --> 21:58.585
HEY, I KNOW
ALL THE BEST REHABS.

21:58.619 --> 22:02.456
I'M TOTALLY ADDICTED
TO THAT SHOW "INTERVENTION."

22:09.997 --> 22:13.200
[ SIGHS ]

22:21.408 --> 22:23.877
I...
[ SIGHS ]

22:23.911 --> 22:26.413
...CAN'T.

22:26.446 --> 22:28.615
HE CAN'T.

22:32.786 --> 22:35.556
WELL, THEN, I WILL.

22:35.589 --> 22:39.026
THANK YOU FOR COMING
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

22:39.059 --> 22:41.962
BUT I FIGURED
WE'RE ALL UNEMPLOYED

22:41.995 --> 22:44.798
AND HAD NOTHING ELSE TO DO,
SO...

22:44.831 --> 22:47.601
I'M CELIA HODES,
TEAM LEADER.

22:50.838 --> 22:55.609
DOUG WILSON, FINANCE,
CO‐TEAM LEADER.

22:55.642 --> 22:58.745
DEAN HODES, LEGAL.

22:58.779 --> 23:02.082
SANJAY PATEL, SALES.

23:02.115 --> 23:06.220
IGNACIO MORELLO JR.,
SUPPLY.

23:07.221 --> 23:09.890
PERRO INSANO, MUSCLE.

23:09.923 --> 23:12.025
[ GROWLS ]
DOWN, BOY.

23:13.994 --> 23:15.896
INTRODUCE YOURSELF.

23:15.929 --> 23:17.197
WE ALL KNOW EACH OTHER.

23:17.231 --> 23:19.933
DO YOU WANT TO PLAY
OR NOT?

23:19.967 --> 23:21.768
FINE.

23:21.802 --> 23:26.340
ISABEL HODES, BRAINS.

23:27.908 --> 23:31.011
I HAVE A TEAM.

23:37.351 --> 23:39.653
I'M GONNA HAVE TO TAKE IT OFF
WHEN I DO SURGERY.

23:39.686 --> 23:43.824
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
TAKE IT OFF IF YOU
DON'T SAY "YES" ALREADY.

23:43.857 --> 23:44.892
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:44.925 --> 23:46.894
SO, WHAT'D YOU AND NANCY
TALK ABOUT?

23:46.927 --> 23:47.928
I DON'T REMEMBER.

23:47.961 --> 23:49.863
I WAS TOO BUSY
THINKING ABOUT YOU.

23:49.897 --> 23:51.298
BULLSHIT.
IT'S TRUE, I WAS.

23:51.331 --> 23:54.268
I WAS THINKING ABOUT
HOW YOU OWE ME AN "I LOVE YOU"

23:54.301 --> 23:57.771
FROM WHEN I SAID IT IN THE HALL
OUTSIDE THE JUNKIE'S ROOM.

23:57.804 --> 24:00.007
WELL, IN THAT CASE,
I LOVE YOU.

24:00.040 --> 24:01.942
Gayle:
I LOVE YOU MORE.

24:01.975 --> 24:05.045
HAVE A SEAT, SINNERS.

24:09.049 --> 24:11.084
[ SIGHS ]

24:18.058 --> 24:21.094
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

24:24.965 --> 24:26.967
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

24:30.103 --> 24:34.441
MOM ARRANGED IT FOR HER
TO GO SOMEPLACE IN ARIZONA.

24:34.474 --> 24:36.176
SHE'S ON THE PLANE NOW.

24:36.210 --> 24:38.579
IT WAS WEIRD
SEEING ESTEBAN CRY.

24:38.612 --> 24:39.746
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:39.780 --> 24:41.882
FUCKING IDIOTS.

24:41.915 --> 24:43.684
SLOW DOWN THERE,
COWBOY.

24:43.717 --> 24:44.885
I ENJOY THE BUBBLES.

24:44.918 --> 24:47.187
I'M NOT GONNA BECOME
AN I. V. DRUG USER.

24:47.221 --> 24:47.988
NO.

24:48.021 --> 24:50.357
YOU LIKE PAIN TOO MUCH.

24:50.390 --> 24:53.760
WHY DIDN'T
YOU GO TO EUROPE?

24:55.596 --> 24:59.233
'CAUSE IT LOOKED LIKE YOU WERE
GONNA GO OFF THE DEEP END,

24:59.266 --> 25:01.768
AND I WANTED TO BE AROUND
TO JUMP IN.

25:01.802 --> 25:03.837
YOU SHOULD GO.
I'LL BE FINE.

25:03.871 --> 25:06.740
[ CHUCKLES ]
WE'LL SEE.

25:06.773 --> 25:09.743
THERE'S ALSO MOM
TO WORRY ABOUT.

25:09.776 --> 25:11.445
THE TEFLON WARRIOR?

25:11.478 --> 25:14.681
ONE DAY,
HER LUCK'S GONNA RUN OUT.

25:19.486 --> 25:22.523
YOU HAVING A GOOD TIME?

25:22.556 --> 25:25.459
THE TUNA POKE IS GOOD.

25:25.492 --> 25:27.794
GET USED TO IT.

25:27.828 --> 25:29.429
GET USED TO TUNA POKE?

25:29.463 --> 25:30.898
GET USED TO THE ROLE
YOU'RE PLAYING.

25:30.931 --> 25:33.567
GET USED TO PILAR
AND HER WAYS.

25:33.600 --> 25:36.270
I'M NOT PREPARED TO GET USED TO
PILAR AND HER WAYS.

25:36.303 --> 25:37.137
NO?

25:37.171 --> 25:39.640
WELL, WHAT A BAD GIRL SCOUT
YOU ARE.

25:39.673 --> 25:41.675
I'VE PREPARED
IN OTHER WAYS.

25:41.708 --> 25:43.577
HAVE YOU NOW?

25:43.610 --> 25:45.379
OH, MINI SLIDERS.

25:45.412 --> 25:48.549
YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULD GET ONE
BEFORE YOU HAVE TO GO.

25:50.317 --> 25:53.220
YEAH.
WE'LL TALK ABOUT IT LATER.

25:55.856 --> 25:57.124
NO, NO.

25:57.157 --> 25:59.126
NO, NO, NO, NO.
COME.

26:02.763 --> 26:04.831
I'M SORRY, NANCY.

26:04.865 --> 26:08.302
I'M SORRY
ABOUT EVERYTHING.

26:10.370 --> 26:12.840
IT'S LIFE.

26:12.873 --> 26:14.775
THAT'S WHAT SHANE TOLD ME.

26:14.808 --> 26:16.810
SOMETHING HAPPENS TODAY,

26:16.844 --> 26:18.679
SOMETHING ELSE
WILL HAPPEN TOMORROW.

26:20.881 --> 26:23.016
YEAH.

26:23.050 --> 26:26.386
WAIT.
IT'S COLD OUTSIDE.

26:26.420 --> 26:28.956
HERE.

26:28.989 --> 26:31.325
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE,
YOU KNOW?

26:31.358 --> 26:34.494
TELL THE BOYS I'LL MEET THEM
IN THE CAR?

26:34.528 --> 26:37.264
YOU'RE TRUSTING ME
WITH YOUR KIDS?

26:37.297 --> 26:39.666
[ SIGHS ]
WE'RE ALL BROKEN.

26:42.569 --> 26:43.971
I KNOW.
MY TIME IS UP.

26:44.004 --> 26:46.640
WHY DON'T WE
TAKE A WALK FIRST?

26:46.673 --> 26:47.841
YOU LOOK NICE.

26:47.875 --> 26:50.978
WELL, THANK YOU.
YOU LOOK NICE, TOO.

26:51.011 --> 26:53.847
SO, GUILLERMO.

26:53.881 --> 26:55.716
INTERESTING CHOICE.

26:56.950 --> 26:58.752
GUILLERMO?

