I HAD TO LEAVE EARLY.

27:17.738 --> 27:19.106
OH...
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:19.139 --> 27:22.209
YOUR PRESS‐ON NAILS
ARE DIGGING INTO MY ARM.

27:22.242 --> 27:23.577
YOU THINK THIS IS A JOKE?

27:23.610 --> 27:26.180
YOU TOOK A FUCKING SHOT AT ME
AND YOU HIT MY KID

27:26.213 --> 27:28.015
