FOR PHOTOS,

27:38.292 --> 27:43.931
BUT, UH, SILAS AND SHANE ‐‐
THEY ARE ‐‐ WHAT'S THE WORD?

27:43.964 --> 27:45.132
EXTRANEOUS.

27:46.700 --> 27:49.536
WE DON'T NEED THEM TO COMPLETE
OUR PRETTY PICTURES.

27:49.570 --> 27:53.941
YOU COME ANYWHERE NEAR MY
CHILDREN, I'LL KILL YOU MYSELF.

27:53.974 --> 27:56.076
YOU LOOK
STUNNING IN BLACK.

27:56.109 --> 27:58.879
THE PEOPLE
WILL BE VERY SYMPATHETIC

27:58.912 --> 28:00.681
TOWARD THE GRIEVING MOTHER

28:00.714 --> 28:05.485
WHO HAS JUST LOST HER BEAUTIFUL
CHILDREN IN A TRAGIC...

28:05.519 --> 28:06.787
CAR ACCIDENT?

28:06.820 --> 28:09.656
OR PERHAPS A...
PLANE CRASH.

28:09.690 --> 28:11.525
OR PERHAPS ‐‐
[ GASPS ]

28:13.227 --> 28:15.095
Shane:
A CROQUET MALLET?

28:16.230 --> 28:19.066
